data.description: Welcome to this adorable 3 bed, 2 bath ranch near Fairmount Park is ready for new owners! Total makeover from top to bottom w/ fresh paint on interior & exterior, refinished hardwood floors, new LVP flooring, updated plumbing, and remodeled kitchen and baths. Main floor includes living room, formal dining, kitchen, 2 bedrooms, and a full bathroom. Plenty of storage space w/ pull-down attic access. Basement features additional living space, 3rd bedroom w/ egress, a gorgeous 3/4 Bath, laundry area, and a room framed for storage that could potentially be made into a 4th non-conforming bedroom. Enjoy privacy on the large cedar deck overlooking the woods. The backyard is fenced in with direct access to the 1 car garage w/ new siding.
